docs.abstract: Happy Rockefeller, whose marriage to New York Gov Nelson A Rockefeller in 1963 may have caused him to lose Republican presidential nomination, dies at age 88; Rockefellers had both been recently divorced at time of their marriage, which caused controversy at the time.
